<subSubSection id="C370652AFF8D5B7CFF7AA2C6FE79F96D" pageId="23" pageNumber="412" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BD536A1FF8D5B7CFF7AA2C6FE1DF9D5" blockId="23.[242,1475,1445,1746]" pageId="23" pageNumber="412">DESCRIPTION. — Shell ovate fusiform, thin, subtranslucent. Protoconch paucispiral, wide, dome-shaped, smooth. Spire moderate-sized, triangular, blunt, whorls weakly convex. Aperture wide, very oblique, widening slightly towards base, nearly parallel-sided. Base faintly tapering. Outer lip thin, weakly arched, subvertical, shoulder sloping, faintly angled at contact with last whorl, rounded, outer margin narrow, rounded, stepped, inner edge smooth. Four thin columellar plaits, very oblique, lower one long, subvertical, weakly angled over anterior part, 3 upper ones decreasing in size posteriorly.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BD536A1FF8D5B7CFE98A116FDA5F932" blockId="23.[242,1475,1445,1746]" box="[272,524,1653,1677]" pageId="23" pageNumber="412">Colour whitish (faded).</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BD536A1FF8D5B7CFE98A1F4FDE2F910" blockId="23.[242,1475,1445,1746]" box="[272,587,1687,1711]" pageId="23" pageNumber="412">
Dimensions: 5.10 x 
